<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; color:#000000; bEditID:r3st1; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><b><font color="#cc0000">Hey there&nbsp;{!Contact.Name},&nbsp;</font></b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><b><br></b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><b>Tomorrow is our 'Learn to be a Leader' event with the Bromley Army Reserves! Here is an overview of what the day will involve:&nbsp;</b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><b><br></b></div><div style="text-align: center;"><b><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">1. A tour of the Army Barracks which will include artillery and an&nbsp;</span>introduction<span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;to the regiment and the role of an Army Reservist.</span></font></b></div><div style="text-align: center;"><br></div><div style="text-align: center;"><b><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">2.&nbsp;</span>Activities<span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;including a group planning&nbsp;</span>exercise<span style="font-size: 12pt;">, teamwork and&nbsp;</span>initiative<span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;tasks, leadership and command tasks, interviews (based&nbsp;around leadership and confidence skills).</span></font></b></div><div style="text-align: center;"><b><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br></span></font></b></div><div style="text-align: center;"><b><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">3.&nbsp;</span></font></b><b><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">A talk about life as an Army Reservist and a Q&amp;A session. &nbsp;</span></font></b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><b><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br></span></font></b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><b><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">This is just a very unique and exciting event where you can learn skills from some of the strongest leaders!&nbsp;</span></font></b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><b><br></b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><b><font color="#cc0000">Here is some more information for you:&nbsp;</font></b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><b><br></b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><b><font color="#cc0000">When:</font>&nbsp;Saturday 9th of July (09:45 - 15:30)</b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><b><br></b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><font><b><font color="#cc0000">Where:</font><font color="#cc0000" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </font><font>106 Regiment Royal Artillery, Napier House, Baring Road, Grove Park, London, SE12 0BH.&nbsp;</font></b></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><font color="#cc0000"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><b><font color="#cc0000">The nearest train station is Grove Park</font></b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><b><font color="#cc0000"><br></font></b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><b style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">We will be ordering Dominoes pizza for lunch (yum yum) - do let me know if you have any dietary&nbsp;</b><font face="arial"><b>requirements.&nbsp;</b></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; text-align: center;"><b><font color="#cc0000"><font color="#000000" face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">If you require expenses for your travel to be reimbursed please bring a copy of your&nbsp;</span></font><font face="arial">receipt</font><font color="#000000" face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;on the day with you.&nbsp;</span></font></font></b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><b><br></b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><b>If you have any questions do give me a call on 07876836445. &nbsp;</b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><b><br></b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><b>I look forward to seeing you,&nbsp;</b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><b><br></b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><b>Rhiannon&nbsp;</b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><b><br></b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><b>Graduate Associate Manager&nbsp;</b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><b>07876836445</b></div>]]></td>
